py:395:        bedtime_softening_note = existing.bedtime_softening_note\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:399:        bedtime_softening_note = (\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:400:            f\"{bedtime_softening_note} Apply the requested adjustment without losing the overall calm trajectory.\"\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:403:    if bedtime_goal is not None and key in {\"finale\", \"final_image\"}:\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:404:        bedtime_softening_note = (\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:405:            f\"{bedtime_softening_note} Land this beat in service of the bedtime goal: {bedtime_goal}.\"\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:413:        bedtime_softening_note=bedtime_softening_note,\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:423:    return \"The bedtime hero\"\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:462:        context.bedtime_goal\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:483:                context.selected_pitch.title,\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:484:                context.selected_pitch.hook,\nbackend/app/services/beat_sheet_generation.py:509:    return \"beat sheet validation failed: \" + \", \".join(failed)\nbackend/tests/integration/test_data_layer.py:37:    \"audio_jobs\",\nbackend/tests/integration/test_data_layer.py:41:    \"composition_jobs\",\nbackend/tests/integration/test_data_layer.py:42:    \"composition_segments\",\nbackend/tests/integration/test_data_layer.py:45:    \"pitches\",\nbackend/tests/integration/test_data_layer.py:60:    \"bedtime_notes\",\nbackend/app/worker/README.md:13:tying work to API request threads. Future prompts should register composition and narration handlers\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:2:# Source context lives in the prompt pack:\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:3:# - prompts/base_prompt.md\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:4:# - prompts/12-seed-genres-and-tones.md\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:5:# - prompts/40-genre-selection-api-and-ui.md\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:6:# - prompts/41-tone-selection-api-and-ui.md\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:7:# - prompts/52-bedtime-safety-and-content-guidelines.md\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:11:    description: A bedtime-safe adventure with a clear destination, gentle bravery, and a warm return home.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:12:    bedtime_safety_notes: Keep the journey wondrous rather than perilous; any danger should feel temporary, buffered by helpers, and resolved before sleep.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:16:      bedtime_payoff: The final image should land in shelter, reunion, or visible rest.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:21:        bedtime_notes: Avoid sharp reversals or loud triumph; let discoveries feel luminous and safe.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:38:        bedtime_notes: Keep the hero's courage rooted in reassurance from mentors, companions, or familiar rituals.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:55:        bedtime_notes: Let tension resolve early enough that the ending can linger in calm reflection.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:72:    description: A puzzle-forward bedtime story driven by clues, curiosity, and a reassuring explanation.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:73:    bedtime_safety_notes: Mystery should never feel menacing; clues can be strange, but the world must stay emotionally safe and readable.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:77:      bedtime_payoff: The reveal should repair uncertainty and make the world feel kinder than before.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:82:        bedtime_notes: Keep the unknown intriguing instead of eerie; every clue should feel like an invitation.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:99:        bedtime_notes: Let the investigation happen in familiar spaces with emotionally available companions.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:116:        bedtime_notes: Keep the payoff tender and emotionally soothing, not twisty or shocking.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:134:    bedtime_safety_notes: Keep animal-scale stakes manageable and end with nesting, denning, or other visible signs of safety.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:138:      bedtime_payoff: The ending should emphasize home, family, and rhythmic natural quiet.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:143:        bedtime_notes: Keep humor kind and the mishaps tiny enough that they never feel upsetting.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:160:        bedtime_notes: Favor emotional reassurance, caregiving, and tactile coziness over plot intensity.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:177:        bedtime_notes: Water, wind, and night sounds should soothe rather than unsettle.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:195:    bedtime_safety_notes: Keep interpersonal conflict mild, repair visible, and magic supportive instead of chaotic.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:199:      bedtime_payoff: End with closeness, belonging, and a felt sense of mutual care.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:204:        bedtime_notes: Make support explicit; the characters should feel emotionally available to one another.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:221:        bedtime_notes: Keep the silliness breezy and never mean-spirited; the laugh should settle into calm.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:238:        bedtime_notes: Let hurt feelings be named gently and healed clearly before the ending.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:256:    bedtime_safety_notes: Even when dream logic gets strange, maintain orientation through comforting guides, repeated motifs, and gentle landings.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:260:      bedtime_payoff: The ending should feel like a soft arrival into sleep itself.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:265:        bedtime_notes: Keep scene transitions smooth and reassuring so the surrealism never jars.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:282:        bedtime_notes: Pair every strange image with something grounding like blankets, snacks, or a trusted companion.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:295:          ending_style: surreal details fade into a cozy bedtime tableau\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:299:        bedtime_notes: Minimize plot complexity and favor patterned language, repetition, and soothing imagery.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:316:    description: Science-flavored bedtime stories driven by curiosity, observation, and awe rather than technical complexity.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:317:    bedtime_safety_notes: Keep scientific concepts accessible, reassuring, and emotionally warm; discovery should never become sterile or high-pressure.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:321:      bedtime_payoff: The world feels larger, kinder, and more connected by the end.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:326:        bedtime_notes: Let facts deepen awe and comfort rather than interrupt story flow.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:343:        bedtime_notes: Keep experiments small, reversible, and supported by encouraging adults or peers.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:356:          ending_style: success leads to quiet pride and bedtime wind-down\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:359:        description: Natural science and twilight exploration meet in a mellow, outdoorsy bedtime tone.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:360:        bedtime_notes: Keep the setting legible and friendly, with twilight framed as beautiful rather than ominous.\nbackend/app/services/assets.py:52:        composition_job_id: str | None = None,\nbackend/app/services/assets.py:53:        composition_segment_id: str | None = None,\nbackend/app/services/assets.py:54:    