.md:37:- Use the selected pitch, character sheet, genre, tone, and brief context directly. Do not invent unrelated side plots or extra protagonists.\nbackend/app/ai/prompts/beat_sheet_generation.md:39:- Keep the summaries concrete enough that later outlining and composition can follow them.\nbackend/tests/integration/conftest.py:25:DEFAULT_GCS_AUDIO_BUCKET_NAME = \"storyteller-audio\"\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:6:from app.ai import PitchGenerationAdapter, build_pitch_generation_invocation\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:15:    normalize_optional_pitch_text,\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:43:            \"To finish the journey before bedtime, {hero} must solve a string of small, \"\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:62:            \"It fits {genre} and {tone} by offering bedtime-safe mystery, luminous imagery, \"\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:88:            \"{hero_cap} has to understand what the rhythm is asking for before a small bedtime \"\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:108:            \"bedtime pacing, and a final return that feels earned and calm.\"\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:123:            \"goal, and bedtime-safe suspense that resolves into belonging.\"\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:137:    def generate_pitches(\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:145:        genre_bedtime_safety_notes: str | None = None,\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:148:        tone_bedtime_notes: str | None = None,\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:158:        selected_pitch: ExistingSelectedPitchContext | None = None,\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:166:            genre_bedtime_safety_notes=genre_bedtime_safety_notes,\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:169:            tone_bedtime_notes=tone_bedtime_notes,\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:179:            selected_pitch=selected_pitch,\nbackend/app/services/pitch_generation.py:184:               