uld be playable in-app and downloadable.\ndocs/product-brief.md:74:- AI model family: Gemini 3.1, with backend-owned adapters and centralized model configuration\ndocs/product-brief.md:80:- create and revise a bedtime story plan\ndocs/product-brief.md:82:- generate, play, and download narration audio\nbackend/app/main.py:51:        pitch_generation_adapter = getattr(app.state, \"pitch_generation_adapter\", None)\nbackend/app/main.py:52:        if pitch_generation_adapter is not None:\nbackend/app/main.py:53:            pitch_generation_adapter.close()\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:60:        'Choose the overall bedtime-story lane before the rest of the plan is shaped.',\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:68:        'Store the accepted Save-the-Cat beat sheet for the session.',\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:70:      detail: 'Midpoint needs one more bedtime-soft pass.',\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:76:    raw_brief: 'A lantern-filled harbor bedtime quest.',\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:79:  selected_pitch: {\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:80:    id: 'pitch-1',\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:82:    pitch_index: 0,\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:85:      'A child and an otter guardian follow drifting lanterns across the harbor to return each light before bedtime.',\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:89:  active_composition_job: null,\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:90:  active_audio_job: null,\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:92:  latest_audio_asset: null,\nfrontend/src/app/router.test.tsx:202:        name: 'Pick up where bedtime left off.',\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:178:            pitch_title=aggregate.selected_pitch.title if aggregate.selected_pitch else None,\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:204:        pitch_batches=build_pitch_batch_views(aggregate.pitches),\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.py:205:        selected_pitch=build_pitch_view(aggregate.selected_pitch),\nbackend/app/services/session_hydration.