 cast works for the selected pitch\nbackend/app/ai/prompts/character_generation.md:17:  - `bedtime_safety_notes`: one sentence explaining how the cast keeps tension bedtime-safe\nbackend/app/ai/prompts/character_generation.md:19:  - `protagonist`: a structured character profile with role, goal, flaw, comfort trait, bedtime-safety notes, relationships, and visual anchors\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:66:from app.services.pitch_generation import PitchGenerationService\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:142:    def build_prompt_catalog(self) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:162:def get_story_workflow_tool_prompt_catalog() -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:163:    return get_story_workflow_tool_registry().build_prompt_catalog()\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:174:                    \"Start or restart pitch generation from the current story brief and planning \"\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:178:                job_type=\"story.generate_pitches\",\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:184:                        \"Marks the pitches stage in progress and refreshes downstream staleness.\",\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:190:                executor_name=\"_generate_pitches\",\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:195:                description=\"Refine an existing pitch candidate before the user re-selects it.\",\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:197:                job_type=\"story.refine_pitch\",\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:203:                        \"Keeps the pitches stage in progress while a refined pitch pass runs.\",\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:209:                executor_name=\"_refine_pitch\",\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:214:                description=\"Generate or regenerate character sheets from the selected pitch.\",\nbackend/app/services/story_tools.py:254:                description=\"Generate or revise the Save-the-Cat beat sheet for the chos